    "Nevertheless, the current state of Generative AI implemented in higher educational settings is still under-examined.Xiao et al. [56] identified the existence of a ChatGPT school policy in the top 500 universities according to the Quacquarelli Symonds (QS) World University Rankings, result indicates that of the universities with ChatGPT policies, nearly two third embraced ChatGPT in teaching and learning.",
